21 (c) (1) Except as otherwise provided in this subsection, the rentals, rates, fees,
22 tolls, and other charges and revenues are not subject to supervision or regulation by any
23 instrumentality, agency, or unit of this State or any of its political subdivisions.
24 (2) This subtitle does not permit the exercise of any power or the
25 undertaking of any activity that would conflict with the provisions and limitations of the
26 federal Urban Mass Transportation Act of 1964.
27 (3) Tolls for the use of the bridge carrying the John F. Kennedy Memorial
28 Highway over the Susquehanna River may not be less than the comparable tolls charged
29 for the use of the Susquehanna River Bridge.
